ns in the short mixing time regime suggest\nthat some sensitivity to cell body diameter might be retrieved, although\nadditional experiments would be required to further support this statement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2019 10:41:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-02"}
