ms into two and trigger global oscillations in their relative phase. The\noscillations subsequently damp and phase coherence sets in. In the other case,\ntwo independent clouds are suddenly coupled by tunneling. Again, phase\ncoherence emerges between the two subsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2019 14:14:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-02"}
