d in the inertial frame $F$. These predictions\nof the cosmic model are consistent with experiments for small velocities and\nshould be further tested.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2019 15:07:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-06"}
