llowing the use of our interactive learning framework\nwithin a visual analytics system tailored for real-time situational awareness.\nTo demonstrate our framework's effectiveness, we provide domain expert feedback\nfrom first responders who used the extended SMART 2.0 system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2019 09:01:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2019 19:11:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
